    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Single-headed drums in which the main section of the body is goblet-shaped or cylindrical and set upon a slender stem.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
